{"tid":237501,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"Ticketinstock  五月天演唱會  苦主中伏召集區","createTime":"2017-05-10T12:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T13:39:20.000Z","uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4a723e3b511190e0366062affa40b357624848","tid":237501,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:04:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我係3月尾 買左五月天尾場 <br />\n $600飛  計埋佢D 附加費TOTAL @2120/2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經唔係特別平 係四月果時收到個EMAIL 通知話去佢門市拎<br />\n去到四月尾 佢通知我旺角門市比人封左<br />\n要親自係10號去紅館門口搵佢地員工拎飛<br />\n今日去行左幾個圈影都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好啦 去佢地個WEBSITE 有個投訴熱線 打左過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知果幾個電話號碼都話自己係苦主 但佢地只係HOLD飛冇比錢買<br />\n有位苦主更SEND 埋 備案number比我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次買演唱會飛比人呃 去緊差館報警麻煩他苦主都出一出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4R768a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4R768a3.png&h=689fa832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8uDda99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8uDda99.png&h=e22a1177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sobY2G8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsobY2G8.png&h=d0e94006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VAN17hX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVAN17hX.jpg&h=318dde61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"368b41d1b4f2131cd7652e69b0746b72759baf98","tid":237501,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:06:46.000Z","msg":"佢地個website <a href=\"https://www.ticketinstock.com/pages/聯絡本站負責人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketinstock.com%2Fpages%2F%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1%E6%9